===Noun===
'''cunning'''

# [[Aptitude]] in performance; [[skill]], [[proficiency]].
# Skill used in a [[conniving]] matter as to [[deceive]].

===Adjective===
'''cunning'''

#[[Sly]]; [[crafty]]; [[clever]] in [[surreptitious]] behaviour.  
# Cute, appealing. (Rarely used.)
# Skillful. (Antiquated).

